We wash, brush and flush some 78 million gallons of water a day down the drain here. 

@CLTWater has a new plan: Extract a valuable fertilizer from that wastewater stream instead of throwing it away.

What you flush isn't just waste. Read about it here https://ui.uncc.edu/story/charlotte-water-extract-phosphorus-from-wastewater …pic.twitter.com/iLVGrOwoMw

